name: Feature Request
description: Suggest a new feature or enhancement for {{.Name}}
title: "[Feature]: "
labels: ["enhancement", "triage"]
assignees:
  - {{.Organization}}/maintainers
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Thanks for taking the time to suggest a new feature! Please provide as much detail as possible to help us understand your request.

  - type: checkboxes
    id: terms
    attributes:
      label: Prerequisites
      description: Please confirm the following before submitting your feature request
      options:
        - label: I have searched existing issues to ensure this feature hasn't been requested before
          required: true
        - label: I have read the [Contributing Guidelines](../CONTRIBUTING.md)
          required: true
        - label: This feature aligns with the project's goals and scope
          required: true

  - type: dropdown
    id: component
    attributes:
      label: Target Component
      description: Which component would this feature affect?
      options:
        {{if .Components.Frontend.MainApp}}- Frontend - Main App{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Frontend.Home}}- Frontend - Home{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Frontend.Admin}}- Frontend - Admin{{end}}
        - Backend - API Server
        {{if .Components.Mobile.Android}}- Mobile - Android{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Mobile.IOS}}- Mobile - iOS{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Infrastructure.Docker}}- Infrastructure - Docker{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Infrastructure.Kubernetes}}- Infrastructure - Kubernetes{{end}}
        {{if .Components.Infrastructure.Terraform}}- Infrastructure - Terraform{{end}}
        - Documentation
        - CI/CD
        - Developer Experience
        - Multiple Components
        - New Component
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: dropdown
    id: priority
    attributes:
      label: Feature Priority
      description: How important is this feature?
      options:
        - Critical (Essential for core functionality)
        - High (Important for user experience)
        - Medium (Nice to have, improves workflow)
        - Low (Minor enhancement)
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: problem
    attributes:
      label: Problem Statement
      description: What problem does this feature solve? What pain point are you experiencing?
      placeholder: |
        Describe the problem you're trying to solve or the limitation you're facing.
        
        Example: "As a developer, I find it difficult to debug issues because..."
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: solution
    attributes:
      label: Proposed Solution
      description: Describe your proposed solution in detail
      placeholder: |
        Describe how you envision this feature working. Be as specific as possible.
        
        Example: "I would like to see a debug panel that shows..."
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: alternatives
    attributes:
      label: Alternative Solutions
      description: Have you considered any alternative solutions or workarounds?
      placeholder: |
        Describe any alternative approaches you've considered or current workarounds you're using.

  - type: textarea
    id: user_stories
    attributes:
      label: User Stories
      description: Provide user stories that describe how this feature would be used
      placeholder: |
        Example:
        - As a developer, I want to [action] so that [benefit]
        - As an admin, I want to [action] so that [benefit]
        - As an end user, I want to [action] so that [benefit]

  - type: textarea
    id: acceptance_criteria
    attributes:
      label: Acceptance Criteria
      description: What criteria must be met for this feature to be considered complete?
      placeholder: |
        Example:
        - [ ] Feature works in all supported browsers
        - [ ] Feature includes proper error handling
        - [ ] Feature has comprehensive tests
        - [ ] Feature is documented
        - [ ] Feature follows accessibility guidelines

  - type: textarea
    id: mockups
    attributes:
      label: Mockups and Examples
      description: If applicable, provide mockups, wireframes, or examples
      placeholder: |
        Drag and drop images here, paste image URLs, or describe the UI/UX in detail.
        
        You can also reference similar features in other applications.

  - type: textarea
    id: technical_considerations
    attributes:
      label: Technical Considerations
      description: Are there any technical considerations or constraints we should be aware of?
      placeholder: |
        Example:
        - Performance implications
        - Security considerations
        - Compatibility requirements
        - Dependencies on external services
        - Database schema changes

  - type: checkboxes
    id: impact
    attributes:
      label: Impact Assessment
      description: Please check all that apply
      options:
        - label: This feature would benefit multiple user types
        - label: This feature would improve performance
        - label: This feature would enhance security
        - label: This feature would improve accessibility
        - label: This feature would reduce maintenance overhead
        - label: This feature would improve developer experience

  - type: dropdown
    id: breaking_changes
    attributes:
      label: Breaking Changes
      description: Would this feature introduce any breaking changes?
      options:
        - "No breaking changes"
        - "Minor breaking changes (with migration path)"
        - "Major breaking changes (requires major version bump)"
        - "Unsure"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: migration_path
    attributes:
      label: Migration Path
      description: If this feature introduces breaking changes, describe the migration path
      placeholder: |
        How would existing users migrate to use this new feature?
        What deprecation timeline would you suggest?

  - type: checkboxes
    id: research
    attributes:
      label: Research and References
      description: Please check if you have done any of the following research
      options:
        - label: I have researched how similar features are implemented in other projects
        - label: I have considered the impact on existing users
        - label: I have thought about backwards compatibility
        - label: I have considered the maintenance burden

  - type: textarea
    id: references
    attributes:
      label: References and Links
      description: Provide any relevant links, documentation, or references
      placeholder: |
        - Link to similar features in other projects
        - Relevant documentation or specifications
        - Related issues or discussions
        - Research papers or articles

  - type: dropdown
    id: willing_to_implement
    attributes:
      label: Implementation
      description: Are you willing to help implement this feature?
      options:
        - "Yes, I can implement this feature"
        - "Yes, I can help with implementation"
        - "Yes, I can help with testing"
        - "Yes, I can help with documentation"
        - "No, I cannot contribute to implementation"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: timeline
    attributes:
      label: Proposed Timeline
      description: When would you like to see this feature implemented?
      placeholder: |
        Example:
        - Next minor release (within 1-2 months)
        - Next major release (within 3-6 months)
        - Future release (6+ months)
        - No specific timeline

  - type: textarea
    id: additional_context
    attributes:
      label: Additional Context
      description: Add any other context, screenshots, or information about the feature request
      placeholder: |
        Any additional information that might be helpful for understanding or implementing this feature.